txt.en: You have recovered the wine-flasks from the goblins who stole them and picked the remaining grapes. You should now confront the goblin leader, Pampraush.
Pick the grape clusters from the vines ([placeholder]/[placeholder])

'Ah very good! You have done all that I could ask. Thank you for your efforts. Those wicked creatures will learn better than to raid my wine-cellars in the future! And thank you for the remaining grapes. Years from now, your efforts today will bring great joy to many. Hard work brings satisfaction, not just in wine-making but in all things.'
